Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.90,0:00:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都這節骨眼了  我這是幹嘛呢\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那一下傷到腳了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內心深處在恐懼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口出狂言之後  結果就這點出息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實驗開始時間是8時30分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要趕快了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧  偏在這種時候死機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你們不是所有人都互相聯通的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次的實驗我已經劇透不少了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好歹長長記性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.55,0:01:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種情況  實驗會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.52,0:01:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…怎麼…會在這…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你別把無關平民帶來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那接下來應該是將知曉秘密的人滅口的固定情節了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離她遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:01:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…我叫你馬上離御坂妹妹遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽不見嗎  雜碎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為…什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛才說什麼  讓我離遠點?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你算老幾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:04:02.90,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(596,640)}<LEVEL 5>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:04:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢對著被稱為超能力者中頂點的我如此放肆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為你是天王老子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廢話少說  我叫你離她遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.51,0:04:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離她遠點是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可要接好咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好險…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是…做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂問道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難以理解你的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂是只要有必要的器材和藥物的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需按一下鈕就能自動生產的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體是製造出來的  心靈也是借來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.85,0:05:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單價18萬日元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:06.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩餘庫存9968個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了這種東西你何必…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那些無關
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是製造出來的身體還是借來的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些破事無所謂的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是為了救獨一無二的你而來這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還有一堆牢騷要對你發呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以別死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…不行…御坂說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼  狗血煽情劇完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直都在做這種事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:53.29,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(678,642)}<Sisters>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傍晚巷道的妹妹也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你看見那玩意了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.01,0:05:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血流操作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是第一次做  不過還挺不錯的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過人居然有那麼多血啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦不對  那是偶人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾以為你或許是被迫參加實驗計劃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來並非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就揍得你再也幹不了這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點都不夠看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.13,0:06:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憑你那速度  還早了100年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒能阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.26,0:07:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明必須要阻止他的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許他能理所當然般的做到我做不到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這預感毫無根據
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候的貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我分不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們也是  外表雖然一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但都有著生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及  我有不能交由他人的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先得正視自己的心意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:37.17,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(715,645)}<LEVEL 0>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你該不會是無能力者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你說得那麼兇  我還以為是有多了不起的能力者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果就只是像個笨蛋一樣傻衝過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,垃圾中的垃圾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.03,0:08:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直自以為了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了最強的位置來找上我的白癡要多少有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要拗掉一隻手腳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.03,0:09:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們無一例外立刻就理解你這種愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露出後悔與恐懼的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可這傢伙卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你該不會沒有意識到自己是最弱的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼想死的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:26.39,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(828,640)}<Objet>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就如你愿把你變成有趣的屍體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這集裝箱裡好像裝的是麵粉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且今天這個無風狀態也很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這說不定會很危險哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.73,0:09:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲  渣渣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道粉塵爆炸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我都差點掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒了氧氣我也會難受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來不能對外宣稱我連核彈攻擊都不怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是  你擺起架勢準備幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.28,0:10:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆炸?  難道他…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  不能把你也牽連進來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你該為你的無能感到慶幸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弱成你這樣  我的反射都不能好好工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.39,0:10:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  我覺得你已經盡力了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:03.49,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(574,642)}<Accelerator>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟在一方通行大爺面前還有氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.88,0:11:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你差不多該解脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨便選隻手摸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅僅是這樣就能讓你的血液
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的身體電流逆流而死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要哪邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左  還是右
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是兩邊都要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月亮?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼在看月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我躺著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我又怎麼會倒在地上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才還在我面前呢  怎麼跑那麼遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  那傢伙為什麼能四肢健全地站著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事  好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛覺?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被揍飛了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在碰到我之前  他的手就應該斷了才對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.58,0:12:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為把注意力集中到了雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無意識間就關掉了身上的反射嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思  靠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好到爆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就愉快的死個漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:12.60,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,646)}<Accelerator>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他壓制著一方通行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對方可是學園都市最強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是毫無關係的陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算逃掉也不會有人責備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.85,0:13:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要將那個約定…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帳  扭來扭去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那右手是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別太囂張了  渣渣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你做這種無聊的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:07.38,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(459,646)}<Sisters>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹她們也是在拼命的活著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竭盡全力地…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憑什麼要為了你這種傢伙而做犧牲品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活著?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說過「她們是偶人」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足以讓這傢伙閉嘴的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是足以支配道理與規則的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.44,0:15:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼突然間…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空氣  風  大氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.78,0:15:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能殺掉面前這雜碎的子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果用這隻手抓住大氣中的流動風向的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能將全世界的流動風向都納入手中的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就算毀滅世界也是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學園都市最強?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:06.21,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,642)}<LEVEL 6>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對能力?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些東西我已經不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界上已經再也沒有什麼能阻止我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界盡在我手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壓縮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將空氣壓縮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  想到個好玩的點子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼這副衰樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起來啊  最弱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不多陪陪我  我可就虧大了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:39.18,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(642,646)}<Accelerator>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一方通行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手…御坂…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他還有氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.77,0:16:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不能實現你的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我要是死了的話  實驗會就此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有點自作主張
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.47,0:17:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我還希望你能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:28.44,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(829,645)}<Plasma>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將風凝聚於一點而產生的高電離氣體!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想要將這一帶全都毀滅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.25,0:17:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在他眼中連隻螻蟻都算不上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他現在一定只對嘗試自己的新力量感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.78,0:17:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦  要怎麼辦才…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將學園都市的風凝聚於一點?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:54.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只要用城市裡的那個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是要怎麼做…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:17:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一個人的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了  醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.47,0:18:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底還期望這狀態下的她做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我是在強人所難
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道這個請求很殘忍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我還想讓你幫忙做件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是只有你才能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為什麼會這麼弱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一個人是保護不了大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:44.53,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(725,645)}<Ace>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學園都市的王牌?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:46.87,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(722,645)}<LEVEL 5>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅有七人的超能力者?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是什麼都做不到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:54.22,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(836,642)}<Accelerator>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治不好她的傷  阻止不了一方通行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也實現不了他的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守護他的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我難以理解那句話的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不知道為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那句話響徹我的心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像自己的身體一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像活動自己的手腳一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.78,0:19:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支配整個空間的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來和強者打是升級捷徑這說法不假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.69,0:19:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  渣渣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會飽含感激之意將你不留痕跡地…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:54.60,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(564,642)}<Plasma>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高電離氣體正在擴散
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的計算不會出錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  這怎麼看都不是自然風
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.21,0:20:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝了  接下來就交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該還是能創造出讓他們逃走的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.87,0:20:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果妨礙目標的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能讓目標的注意力轉移到御坂身上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就趁機和那個少年逃離這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  這可是姐姐的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這風到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風力操作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.02,0:20:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  風車在逆轉?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  我聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給發電機的馬達加以特殊電磁波的話就會旋轉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡  不過到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些風車並不是在胡亂轉動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了擾亂我的計算式而被統一操作著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她通過網絡將所見的影像給…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滅了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是玩弄我好幾次了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.47,0:21:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為人類服從著由機器所制定的政策
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了我死以外已別無他法了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.67,0:21:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫幫我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶人  最弱  Original
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.47,0:23:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我不會讓你們再阻撓我了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.55,0:23:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我一定要得到無敵的力量
